# Test 1 — Tracked Output

Tracked output for the drone footage sequence (280 frames @ 24 fps, 3840×2160).

The silver car roof provides sparse Harris corners (~67 at initialisation). The velocity-guided
background filter suppresses competing road-marking corners and stabilises tracking by frame 90.
100% tracker stability maintained across all 280 frames.

